
Hardware configuration declarations :

Example :
        Intake intake_motor expansion hub motor port 3

        Major Arm major_arm_motor expansion hub motor port 2
        Major Claw major_claw_servo expansion hub servo port 0

        Minor Arm major_arm_servo expansion hub motor port 2
        Major Claw major_claw_servo expansion hub servo port 0

        Elevator elevator_motor control hub motor port 2
        Magazine magazine_servo control hub servo port 0

        Spinner spinner_motor control hub motor port 3

        Drive motors:
        Front Right Motor frmotor expansion hub motor port 0
        Back Right Motor brmotor expansion hub motor port 1
        Back Left Motor blmotor control hub motor port 0
        Front Left Motor flmotor control hub motor port 1
